{"type": "article", "id": 11599, "title": "“BENT”椅子系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-03T11:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141159PGZ9w7H4ogV5Qkvj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t荷兰设计师 Tristan Frencken 最近推出了一个名为 “BENT” 的椅子系列，这些看上去充满上个世纪 50 年代经典设计风格的椅子，因为材料的更新，颜色的选择和巧妙加入的笑眯眯的“眼睛”而充满乐趣。这套作品由餐椅，休闲椅和桌子三件组成，既适用室内，也可以和室外环境相配。设计师甚至给它们做了“小衣服”，让椅子的体验能够更舒适一些。<a href=\"http://www.tristanfrencken.com/design/bent-collection-tristan-frencken\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135723AyEtKbj0knJSYRsV.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"792\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135724tLKATZmalINb0Oiw.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"367\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261357249BVcJXRStMnm7W2x.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135725t3XDHW7T2QlI5gLi.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"357\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.595\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135725gHpIVqnZjaEuveA5.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"751\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.25166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135726NCWiF3fDOqLAKSJd.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"901\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261357267aEzeJkV0PlSdicA.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" title=\" \" 